title: Companies on the Norwegian insurance market 2011 to 2015
summary: Overall Domestic market, and Total market are roughly constant,  throughout the Year
The order of lines according to average values of Number of companies, in descending order is: 1. Total market, and lastly, 2. Domestic market.
The difference of Number of companies between Domestic market and Total market is roughly same at Year 2014 compared to the Year 2013.
